<p>

<b>WASHINGTON, D.C. --</b> Live from Washington, D.C., <b>Gary
L. Bauer</b> -- Family Research Council president and domestic
policy adviser to Ronald Reagan -- will be available for comment
as the Democratic National Convention takes to the airways August
26 to 29.

