<DOCOLDNO>IA069-000434-B010-40</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservative.org:80/nationalreview/extra/082896x.html 204.71.237.88 19970208171631 text/html 13677
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 17:17:18 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 00:23:40 GMT
