http://www.conservative.org:80/ads/renew/ 204.71.237.88 19970208073421 text/html 2838
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 07:35:04 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 22-Dec-95 15:00:55 GMT
