<p>

<li>David Wood. &quot;Drill Sergeants Sound Off.&quot; <i>The Detroit 
News and Free Press</i>. 20 May 1995:1A.

<p>

<li>&quot;Report to the President.&quot; <i>Op. cit.</i>, p. 52.

<p>

<li><i>Ibid</i>., p. 5.

<p>

<li><i>Ibid</i>., p. 9.

<p>

<li><i>Ibid</i>., p. 13.

<p>

<li><i>Ibid</i>., p. 11.

<p>

<li>Larry Tye. &quot;Exercise Your Judgment.&quot;  <i>The Boston Globe</i>. 
7 March 1995:63.

<p>

<li>Ira Dreyfuss. &quot;Too Much Exercise, Too Little Eating May Hurt 
Reproductive Ability.&quot; <i>The Associated Press</i>. 5 November 1995.

<p></ol></font>

